        "subject": "LU-6245 lustre: include kthread.h",
        "message": "LU-6245 lustre: include kthread.h\n\nSoon the libcfs wrappers for linux primitives will be removed\nand any code needed to use kthread will need to include the\nlinux header kthread.h. While testing DNE2 along side the\nlibcfs cleanup kthread.h was missing so this patch adds the\nneeded header to avoid a potential build issues when both\nworks will land.\n\nChange-Id: I6d4f88d4f8517b0e150f04b5a08b07614b8c7bf5\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@yahoo.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
